---
import { Anim } from "../components/AnimatedCharacter";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
// The Idea Factory üè≠ is a community of students who take
//                    risks to create something new.
---

<Layout title="Manifesto - the idea factory">
  <div
    style="background: hsla(9, 100%, 56%, 1), hsla(220, 94%, 52%, 1), hsla(274, 100%, 51%, 1);"
    class="container mx-auto max-w-screen-xl py-24 p-4"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-16 py-16">
        <Anim client:load />

        <p class="text-2xl">
          We help students turn their ideas into real products. We provide the
          tools, mentorship, and community to help you build your idea. We are
          here to help you learn the skills you need to become a successful
          entrepreneur.
          <br />
          <br />
        </p>
      </div>
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1454360/pexels-photo-1454360.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1"
        alt="Students working on a project"
        class="w-full aspect-[16/7] object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="py-24 p-4 bg-white">
    <div class="prose container mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Our story</h3>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 justify-between w-full items-start"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 max-w-screen-md">
          <p>
            The Idea Factory was founded by a group of experienced business
            professionals who recognized a growing need for mentorship and
            resources for aspiring entrepreneurs. Fueled by a shared passion for
            innovation and a desire to help young visionaries thrive, they set
            out to create a platform that would provide comprehensive support to
            startups.
          </p>

          <p>
            Through dedication and hard work, they established a community of
            entrepreneurs, mentors, and industry experts committed to fostering
            excellence, collaboration, and growth. By providing access to a
            diverse range of resources, from seed funding to networking
            opportunities, they have helped numerous startups achieve their
            business goals and drive their industries forward.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 max-w-screen-md">
          <p>
            Despite the challenges of the startup landscape, The Idea Factory
            remains committed to its mission of empowering the next generation
            of business leaders. Its passionate and experienced team of mentors
            and professionals will continue to work tirelessly to build a
            platform that empowers startups to succeed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="py-24 p-4">
    <div class="prose container mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Our approach</h3>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 justify-between w-full items-start"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 w-full">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <p>
              At The Idea Factory, we have designed a comprehensive approach
              that empowers startups to thrive in the competitive business
              landscape. Our multifaceted approach encompasses hackathons,
              mentoring, workshops, provision of cloud and dev resources,
              collaboration, networking, and strategic partnerships with
              experts, lecturers, and industry leaders.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl">Expert Guidance for Lasting Success</h4>
            <p>
              We understand that the road to success can be complex and
              intimidating. That's why we provide startups with a network of
              seasoned mentors, experts who have traversed the path themselves.
              Our mentors offer personalized guidance, imparting their
              invaluable insights, proven strategies, and industry wisdom.
              Through one-on-one mentoring sessions, startups gain clarity,
              expand their perspectives, and receive tailored advice on refining
              their business strategies. With the guidance of our experienced
              mentors, entrepreneurs confidently steer their ventures towards
              sustainable growth and long-term success.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl">
              Equipping Entrepreneurs with Essential Skills
            </h4>
            <p>
              Continuous learning is at the core of entrepreneurial success. Our
              dynamic workshops cover a diverse range of topics, from market
              research and financial planning to product development and
              marketing strategies. Led by industry professionals, these
              workshops provide startups with practical knowledge, cutting-edge
              methodologies, and hands-on tools to sharpen their skills. By
              attending these immersive sessions, entrepreneurs gain the
              confidence and competence they need to navigate challenges, seize
              opportunities, and build a robust foundation for their businesses.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl">Empowering Digital Transformation</h4>
            <p>
              In the digital age, embracing technology is vital for startups to
              thrive. To support entrepreneurs in their tech-driven ambitions,
              we provide access to cutting-edge cloud services and development
              resources. Startups can leverage these provisions for hosting,
              storage, and development tools. By removing the barriers to entry
              for digital innovation, we enable startups to focus on what they
              do best ‚Äì creating and scaling disruptive technologies that
              redefine industries. foundation for their businesses.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h4 class="text-xl">
              Amplifying Potential through Strategic Alliances
            </h4>
            <p>
              We understand the power of collaborative ecosystems. That's why we
              partner with esteemed experts, lecturers, and industry leaders who
              share our vision of driving innovation. These strategic
              partnerships provide startups with additional resources,
              mentorship, and exposure, giving them a competitive edge in the
              market. By joining forces with renowned figures in the industry,
              startups can tap into a vast network of opportunities, gain
              industry insights, and propel their growth towards unprecedented
              heights.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-zinc-200 p-8 flex flex-col gap-2 max-w-sm w-full drop-shadow-sm lg:sticky top-4"
        >
          <p class="text-zinc-950 text-sm uppercase">
            You should reach out to us if:
          </p>
          <p>
            <ul class="list-disc">
              <li>
                You are a student who wants to learn how to build a real
                product.
              </li>
              <li>
                You are an expert in your field and want to help others learn
                industrial skills.
              </li>
              <li>
                You are a company that wants to hire students who have real
                world experience.
              </li>
              <li>
                You are an investor who wants to invest in student startups.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="py-24 p-4 bg-white">
    <div class="prose mx-auto max-w-screen-xl container">
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">It all starts with an idea and a great team</h3>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 justify-between w-full items-start"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <p>
            It all starts with the idea, the product, the vision and the team.
            No one has ever done it, its so painfully obvious, can you build it?
            Yes! We can help you build it. We are here to help you learn the
            skills you need to become a successful entrepreneur.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <h4 class="text-xl">Vision</h4>
            <p>
              We have a vision of a world where everyone has the opportunity to
              learn the skills they need to become a successful entrepreneur.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <h4 class="text-xl">Mission</h4>
            <p>
              We are here to help you learn the skills you need to become a
              successful entrepreneur. Through our comprehensive programs,
              mentorship, and access to a vibrant entrepreneurial community, we
              aim to foster a culture of innovation, drive, and resilience.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <h4 class="text-xl">Core values</h4>
            <p>
              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>
                  Integrity: We are honest and transparent in all our dealings.
                </li>
                <li>Excellence: We strive to be the best at what we do.</li>
                <li>
                  Innovation: We are always looking for new ways to do things
                  better.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Community: We believe that the best way to learn is by doing,
                  and that the best way to do is by working with others.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Collaboration: We believe that the best way to work with
                  others is to be part of a community.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            These values guide our actions and decisions as we work towards our
            mission of empowering innovators and building future leaders.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-sm w-full flex flex-col gap-8">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 p-8 flex flex-col gap-2">
            <p class="text-zinc-950 text-sm uppercase font-">
              Unleash your potential
            </p>
            <p class="text-blue-950">
              We are committed to nurturing and empowering individuals with
              groundbreaking ideas, providing them with the resources, guidance,
              and support they need to turn their dreams into reality.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-orange-100 p-8 flex flex-col gap-2">
            <p class="text-zinc-950 text-sm uppercase font-">
              Empowering Innovators, Building Future Leaders
            </p>
            <p class="text-orange-950">
              We strive to provide a platform that enables ambitious individuals
              to transform their ideas into successful businesses.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="p-4">
    <div class="prose py-24 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl container">
      <h3 class="text-3xl mb-4">Driven by the spirit of collaboration</h3>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 justify-between w-full max-w-screen-md"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <p>
            We believe that the best way to learn is by doing, and that the best
            way to do is by working with others. We have partnered with industry
            experts to help you learn the skills you need to become a successful
            entrepreneur.
            <br />
            <br />
            In addition to that we are always looking for partners who can help us
            grow our community. If you are interested in partnering with us, please
            reach out to us at{" "}

            <a href="mailto:hey@tif.co.zw"> hey@tif.co.zw</a>. As a partner you
            will have access to our community of students and will be able to
            help them learn the skills they need to become successful
            entrepreneurs. Partners also get consulation preference and access
            to our network of experts.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="uppercase text-sm font- text-zinc-950">Partners</p>
              <p>
                Patners are selected based on their ability to provide value to
                our community.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-8 items-center">
              <a href="https://cut.ac.zw" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank">
                <img
                  src="https://www.cut.ac.zw/welcome/assets/img/logo.png"
                  class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full"
                  alt="CUT"
                />
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  #banner span:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  #banner span:nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  #banner span:nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }
</style>
